title: Disney Announces Their 2019 Movie Slate With New Synopses and Image Stills Including Captain Marvel
body:
Disney Announces Their 2019 Movie Slate With New Synopses and Image Stills Including Captain Marvel

Walt Disney Studios announced their 2019 movie slate with new stills and synopses from all of their upcoming movies.

Disney will debut eight new movies in 2019. The movies are:

  • Captain Marvel
  • Dumbo
  • Avengers: Endgame
  • Toy Story 4
  • Penguins
  • Artemis Fowl
  • Aladdin
  • Lion King

Take a look at the new official synopses.

title: About that Myth that Marvel Isn't Confident in Captain Marvel...
body:
About that Myth that Marvel Isn’t Confident in Captain Marvel…

Over the last week or so there have been people attempting to spread fear, uncertainty, and doubt about Captain Marvel prior to advance tickets going on sale next week in a pathetic attempt to sabotage the movie in the minds of people online. The catalyst for this latest round of anonymous fanboyism is that the rumoreddate for the red carpet premiere has been found and some people are using that…
